<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="horizon-n">horizon <strong><em>n</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /hə'raɪzn/    美 /hə'raɪzn/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1the">1.<strong>[与the连用] 地平线：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>on / below the horizon</strong>
在地平线上/下</p></div>

<h4 id="2-c">2.★ <strong>[C] [复数] 范围；眼界：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Travel is a kind of study because it broadens one's horizons.
旅游是一种学习，因为它开阔人们的视野。</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">固定搭配</h2>
<h3 id="on-the-horizon">on the horizon</h3>
<p>1.<strong>将要发生</strong>  </p></div>